Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.82,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Atrocious Serial Murder Case\NSpecial Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin with the Public Intelligence report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The total number of reports from the public, including phone calls, currently stands at 3029.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the large majority of them seems to be prank calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been 14 reported incidents of people who either know or have seen Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have investigated these thoroughly, one by one, and I believe that - just as reported - it would be safe to say that none of them have any credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also 21 reported incidents of people claiming to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of those 21 reports has been followed up, and will remain on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving onto the victims..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can confirm that information on all the known victims that died of heart attacks was publicly available in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}we have followed up L's specific request that we investigate the assumed time of death for each victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, we have followed up L's specific request that we investigate the assumed time of death for each victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Results indicate that 68% of all deaths occurred during weekdays, between four in the afternoon and midnight, Japanese time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of deaths peaks over the weekend, when they can occur at any time between eleven in the morning through till late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all extremely interesting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suggests that given the assumed times of death, {\alpha&HFF&}there is a possibility that our culprit may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suggests that given the assumed times of death, there is a possibility that our culprit may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have further grounds to support this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they appear to be only targeting criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}the culprit seems to be motivated by a sense of "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they appear to be only targeting criminals, the culprit seems to be motivated by a sense of "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's conceivable that they may even plan on becoming some kind of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we may be dealing with an extremely hollow psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is mere speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}please rid yourselves of any preconceptions you might have that our culprit cannot be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, please rid yourselves of any preconceptions you might have that our culprit cannot be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To consider every possibility; {\alpha&HFF&}that is likely to be the shortest road to apprehending Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To consider every possibility; that is likely to be the shortest road to apprehending Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue the investigation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other observations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. {\alpha&HFF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to support Kira in any way by saying this..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but over the last few days.. {\alpha&HFF&}throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but over the last few days.. throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. {\alpha&HFF&}the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but over the last few days.. throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.. {\alpha&HFF&}that kind of phenomenon was to be expected..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.. that kind of phenomenon was to be expected..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. L, that concludes today's investigation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. {\alpha&HFF&}I feel that we're one step closer to finding the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. I feel that we're one step closer to finding the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have another order to trouble you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the teams investigating victims, information and Internet to double-check what information regarding each victim was previously released in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More specifically, whether or not footage or photographs of the victims had been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks. {\alpha&HFF&}The late nights are beginning to take their toll on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks. The late nights are beginning to take their toll on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about this now, {\alpha&HFF&}everyone was probably already aware of what I said about crime going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about this now, everyone was probably already aware of what I said about crime going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to speak the truth, no matter what kind of truth it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it's awkward to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if everyone continues to think that Kira should be commended for lowering crime, it will become harder and harder to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Surely no one would commend such a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely no one would commend such a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I could count on you, onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. {\alpha&HFF&}Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like dad's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't you at least try doing the last question yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. After dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have everything in hand, seeing you're able to afford the time to help out with your sister's homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the police were to come after me, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm confident that I have something to fight them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the police were to come after me, I'm confident that I have something to fight them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, {\alpha&HFF&}father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.. Yes, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your studies going, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always. Top of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my older brother! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my son! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem tired, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to say much, {\alpha&HFF&}but this case is proving to be exceedingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to say much, but this case is proving to be exceedingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is part of the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the source of your confidence, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can also access my father's computer without leaving any trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can get hold of all the information regarding the investigation, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the police are already beginning to suspect that the culprit could be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that be risky for you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is not specified, then by default, the person will die of a heart attack."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes 40 seconds are granted to write any further details."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct, isn't it Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you write "heart attack" first, {\alpha&HFF&}you can still write details of their death afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you write "heart attack" first, you can still write details of their death afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll be able to provide you with some more entertainment, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}There were another 23 victims yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There were another 23 victims yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were 23 victims the day before that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All spaced out evenly, one every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that this has continued over two weekdays must mean..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theory that the culprit could be a student is weakened..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone can potentially skip two days of school..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the likelihood of them being a student has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is not what Kira is trying to say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have they spaced the killings at precisely one hour intervals?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, {\alpha&HFF&}why are the victims all prisoners that could be found quickly after their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, why are the victims all prisoners that could be found quickly after their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is trying to tell us.. {\alpha&HFF&}that they can control the time of death at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is trying to tell us.. that they can control the time of death at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility that Kira could be a student was put forward, {\alpha&HFF&}the timing of the murders change to indicate that this was not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility that Kira could be a student was put forward, the timing of the murders change to indicate that this was not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}the timing is too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the timing is too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira must have access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly... {\alpha&HFF&}a direct challenge to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly... a direct challenge to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that L will probably begin to sweat a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have 50 criminals that I've deliberately left alive for a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, thanks to the last few incidents L should be beginning to suspect someone in, or connected to, the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has a way of getting police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fact can no longer be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kira's final objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, showing them that you have connections to the police place you at a greater disadvantage than having them suspect Kira of being a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is, {\alpha&HFF&}I did it to help me find and destroy L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is, I did it to help me find and destroy L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are very few people who actually trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even amongst the police force.. {\alpha&HFF&}and especially between the police and L, who never had a bond of trust between them from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even amongst the police force.. and especially between the police and L, who never had a bond of trust between them from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you honestly trust someone whose name and face are unknown to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows that I'm getting police information, {\alpha&HFF&}without a doubt, he'll try to find a trail leading to me that starts within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows that I'm getting police information, without a doubt, he'll try to find a trail leading to me that starts within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, it'll only be a matter of time before even the police can't keep quiet with respect to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, L and the police appear to be working together to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, {\alpha&HFF&}L will be investigating the police, and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, L will be investigating the police, {\alpha&HFF&}and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, L will be investigating the police, and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be the one who'll find L.. {\alpha&HFF&}the police will do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be the one who'll find L.. the police will do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll erase him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.. I'll erase him.
Comment: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.41,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz43.681\move(213,98,225,110,0,1941)\t(0,1960,\fscx95\fscy95)}Letter of \Nresignation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, they are letters of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we're moved to a different case, {\alpha&HFF&}we're leaving the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we're moved to a different case, we're leaving the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. {\alpha&HFF&}why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we value our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's theory is that Kira has some ESP-like power that allows them to kill without having to be there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd try to kill those who are trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, I'd try to kill those who are trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if they get caught, they'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already seen this from that incident on TV, {\alpha&HFF&}when Kira killed the "dummy L" after being provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already seen this from that incident on TV, when Kira killed the "dummy L" after being provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But L hasn't even revealed his name, let alone his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That order we received earlier from L, about checking the information released about the victims prior to their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether or not footage or photos of their faces had been released.. {\alpha&HFF&}That turned out to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether or not footage or photos of their faces had been released.. That turned out to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them had their photo published in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike someone we all know; we had to investigate using our police IDs with our photos attached!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without hiding our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could be killed by Kira at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're asking to be re-assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}You! Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You! {\alpha&HFF&}Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You! Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:13:04.30,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve this problem we must first establish the concept that x squared equals large X.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:11.89,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You can then proceed by noting that the quadratic equation in large X is the key to understanding the problem..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had the FBI arrive in Japan four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've begun their investigation of the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the people on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 141 people within the police who have access to information regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people, or people close to them.. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira will definitely be amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people, or people close to them.. Kira will definitely be amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. Got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you not to talk to me in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, in that case, I'll just talk at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna listen, just cover your ears or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways I think the notebook was found by an awesome person, {\alpha&HFF&}because I have to remain by your side until either you or that Death Note expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways I think the notebook was found by an awesome person, because I have to remain by your side until either you or that Death Note expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm not on your side, and I'm not going to be on L's side either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. I'm not on your side, and I'm not going to be on L's side either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much already, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll never say that what you're doing is right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although as your roommate, I may have a few things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying things like this now? {\alpha&HFF&}It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying things like this now? It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore what I'm about to say is not because I'm on Kira's side, {\alpha&HFF&}but because it's giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore what I'm about to say is not because I'm on Kira's side, but because it's giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a human following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been bugging me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, {\alpha&HFF&}but because I'm always following you around, it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, but because I'm always following you around, {\alpha&HFF&}it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, but because I'm always following you around, it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get rid of him as soon as possible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that L has already started to suspect the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever is investigating the police must have large resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have 50 people on the case, {\alpha&HFF&}the chances that they'll suspect I'm Kira are non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have 50 people on the case, the chances that they'll suspect I'm Kira are non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't be looking at me as anything more than a final year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I leave him alone for a few months, {\alpha&HFF&}the probability that I'll be caught might rise above zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I leave him alone for a few months, the probability that I'll be caught might rise above zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I need my stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can figure that out, I can take care of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Let me tell you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... Let me tell you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two very important differences between a Shinigami and a human with a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Shinigami write human names into their Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty talkative today, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Shinigami take human life spans for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take their "life spans"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you take someone due to die at 60, and write their name so they die at 40 instead..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty minus forty, is twenty. {\alpha&HFF&}Those twenty human years are added to that Shinigami's life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty minus forty, is twenty. Those twenty human years are added to that Shinigami's life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as we don't slack off too much, {\alpha&HFF&}a Shinigami can't be killed with a bullet to the head, or a knife through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as we don't slack off too much, a Shinigami can't be killed with a bullet to the head, or a knife through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the differences between a Shinigami and a human with a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a theory about Shinigami that humans haven't heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second difference will probably be even more of an interest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it concerns decreasing life spans rather than increasing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decreasing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami can tell someone's name by just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's eyes {\alpha&HFF&}have the ability to see a person's name and life span by just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's eyes have the ability to see a person's name and life span by just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name and life span?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:01.06,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can see your name and life span right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I converted that into human time, you would know precisely how many human years you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we aren't allowed to tell you that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a huge blabbermouth like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, a Shinigami will never be prevented from killing someone due to not knowing their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they kill someone, they know exactly how much life they're gaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the distinct difference between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if a Shinigami drops a notebook, and a human picks it up.. {\alpha&HFF&}the Shinigami can change that human's eyes into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if a Shinigami drops a notebook, and a human picks it up.. the Shinigami can change that human's eyes into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you agree to the deal passed down for this purpose since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for the eyes of a Shinigami is.. {\alpha&HFF&}half of that human's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for the eyes of a Shinigami is.. half of that human's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of my remaining life span...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, suppose you were to live for another 50 years, that would be reduced to 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a year remaining, you get left with half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But currently given that you're not on my side, or on L's side, {\alpha&HFF&}you won't tell me the names of the people I want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But currently given that you're not on my side, or on L's side, you won't tell me the names of the people I want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you're saying that I can't simply borrow your powers... {\alpha&HFF&}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you're saying that I can't simply borrow your powers... Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. That's one of the rules of the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the price of just half your remaining life span.. {\alpha&HFF&}you could have the eyes of a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the price of just half your remaining life span.. you could have the eyes of a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I'll be able to tell the name of anyone I meet just by looking at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note would become even easier to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. {\alpha&HFF&}What do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. What do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(567,297)}To be continued
